---
title: Mexican Beef & Black Bean Chilli with Avocado & Cucumber Salsa
description: Say hello to the best bean in town, nutrient-packed black beans. They are wholesome and filling and go perfectly in a bowl with garlic rice and an avocado-cucumber salsa. Now it cook up in a fiery sauce to drive home those mouth-watering flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6594a0f7b6e284551035ad2c-99bd1514.jpeg
